NAME:
   datadog-iac-scanner - Scans your Infrastructure as Code configurations

USAGE:
   datadog-iac-scanner [global options] [command [command options]]

COMMANDS:
   scan            Analyzes the content of a repository
   list-platforms  Returns a list of all available platforms
   list-queries    Returns a list of all available query ids
   help, h         Shows a list of commands or help for one command

GLOBAL OPTIONS:
   --log-format string  log format (pretty, json) (default: "pretty")
   --log-level string   minimum log level to display (trace, debug, info, warn, error, fatal, panic, disable) (default: "error")
   --help, -h           show help
